OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FThe late Queen was "very keen" for
OL,7,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor to be
OL,8,Fappointed as the UK trade envoy,
OL,9,Faccording to a memo from the then-
OL,10,Fforeign secretary.
OL,12,FIn a memo addressed to then foreign
OL,13,Fsecretary Robin Cook dated February 25
OL,14,F2000, then-chief executive of British
OL,15,FTrade International, Sir David Wright,
OL,16,Fsaid Queen Elizabeth II's "wish" had
OL,17,Fbeen for Andrew to take on the job.
OL,26,@xD@[OUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
