OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FThe memo was released on Thursday as
OL,7,Fpart of a trove of files related to
OL,8,FAndrew's appointment as the UK trade
OL,9,Fenvoy.
OL,11,FThe former Duke of York faces
OL,12,Faccusations of sharing sensitive
OL,13,Finformation with paedophile Jeffrey
OL,14,FEpstein while serving in the post
OL,15,Fbetween 2001 and 2011.
OL,17,FMinisters agreed in February to
OL,18,Fpublish documents related to his
OL,19,Fappointment to the role, which gave
OL,20,Fhim access to senior government and
OL,21,Fbusiness figures around the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
