PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FIn the memo, Sir Wright wrote: "The
OL,7,FQueen's wish is that the Duke of Kent
OL,8,Fshould be succeeded in this role by
OL,9,Fthe Duke of York. The Duke of Kent is
OL,10,Fto relinquish his responsibilities
OL,11,Faround April next year. That would fit
OL,12,Fwell with the end of the Duke of
OL,13,FYork's active naval career.
OL,15,F"The Queen is very keen that the Duke
OL,16,Fof York should take on a prominent
OL,17,Frole in the promotion of national
OL,18,Finterests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,F"No other member of The Royal Family
OL,7,Fwould be available to succeed the Duke
OL,8,Fof Kent. The Duke of York's adoption
OL,9,Fof his role would seem a natural fit."
OL,11,FThe documents also revealed that
OL,12,FAndrew did not undergo a formal
OL,13,Fvetting or due diligence process
OL,14,Fbefore being appointed as the UK trade
OL,15,Fenvoy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
