OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FThe move comes after the Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats tabled a humble address in
OL,8,FParliament calling for the publication
OL,9,Fof papers relating to Andrew's role,
OL,10,Fincluding any vetting records and
OL,11,Fcorrespondence from Peter Mandelson,
OL,12,Fthe disgraced former ambassador to the
OL,13,FUS.
OL,15,FThe party criticised the number of
OL,16,Fdocuments released by the government
OL,17,Fon Thursday, calling them a "small
OL,18,Fpaper trail."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
