OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FLib Dem chief whip Wendy Chamberlain
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is shocking and deeply
OL,8,Ftroubling that Andrew was appointed to
OL,9,Fthe trade envoy role with no vetting.
OL,10,FNobody should be above such standards.
OL,11,FThis raises serious questions about
OL,12,Fwhy officials and ministers at the
OL,13,Ftime thought that was acceptable.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
