PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,F"The lack of documentation provided is
OL,7,Fitself concerning, as is the time it
OL,8,Fhas taken to get this far. We must get
OL,9,Fthe full files from government without
OL,10,Fdelay, and an explanation about why
OL,11,Fthere is such a small paper trail. And
OL,12,Fthe Government must commit to
OL,13,Fmandatory vetting for all similar
OL,14,Fappointments in future."
OL,16,FDowning Street said more files related
OL,17,Fto Andrew's appointment are to be
OL,18,Fpublished at a future date.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
