OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FA No 10 spokeswoman told reporters:
OL,7,F"We are complying with the humble
OL,8,Faddress and we're publishing those
OL,9,Fdocuments as quickly as possible.
OL,11,F"We're also supporting the police
OL,12,Finvestigation as you would expect.
OL,14,F"And we'll provide the House with any
OL,15,Fother substantive documents we find in
OL,16,Fthe course of that work."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
