CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779447783
OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FAsked whether it was acceptable that
OL,7,Fno vetting was carried out into
OL,8,FAndrew, the spokeswoman said: "We have
OL,9,Ffound no evidence that a formal due
OL,10,Fdiligence or vetting process was
OL,11,Fundertaken, and there's no evidence
OL,12,Fthat this was considered.
OL,14,F"And this is due to the fact that the
OL,15,Frole was a continuation of the royal
OL,16,Ffamily's involvement in trade and
OL,17,Finvestment promotion work following
OL,18,Fthe Duke of Kent's decision to
OL,19,Frelinquish his duties as vice chairman
OL,20,Fof British Trade International."
OL,26,@pD@_OUvD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
