OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FAndrew was arrested in February on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,8,Foffice and later released under
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,FThe former prince became the UK's
OL,12,Fspecial representative for
OL,13,Finternational trade and investment in
OL,14,F2001, but stepped down ten years later.
OL,16,FHe received no salary for the role but
OL,17,Ffaced criticism over the thousands of
OL,18,Fpounds spent on his expenses and
OL,19,Ftravel costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
