OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FAndrew quit from the role the same
OL,7,Fyear he was pictured with his arm
OL,8,Faround Virginia Giuffre, his primary
OL,9,Faccuser, who said she was trafficked
OL,10,Fto the former duke at the home of
OL,11,Fconvicted sex trafficker Ghislaine
OL,12,FMaxwell.
OL,14,FGiuffre claimed she had sex with
OL,15,FAndrew on three occasions, at
OL,16,FMaxwell's London home, at Epstein's
OL,17,FNew York townhouse, and on Epstein's
OL,18,FCaribbean island, Little St James.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
