OL,3,CLate Queen was 'very keen' for Andrew
OL,4,Cto become UK trade envoy, memo reveals
OL,6,FAndrew paid Giuffre millions of pounds
OL,7,Fto settle a civil lawsuit in the US in
OL,8,F2022, despite claiming never to have
OL,9,Fmet her.
OL,11,FHe has consistently and vehemently
OL,12,Fdenied any wrongdoing.
